data.description: This beautiful new home is the perfect size it has 3 bedrooms 2 baths a flowing living room and dining room perfect for entertaining the family. The beautiful spacious kitchen has plenty of storage and space to prepare meals. The master bath as a huge soaking tub with a separate shower. Grill out on the covered back porch and relax. This home is in a great location and must see!
